(10, '4. Workflows  -  4.7 Filtering ideas', '<p id="docs-internal-guid-933cfa6a-e8ab-e5d7-86ff-30060ff6ec7c" dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">If you see to filter down by category values, you can use the filters located on the search page.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">Step 1: </span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">To search for an idea, click the </span><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">Search</span><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;"> button located on the navbar.</span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;"><img style="border: none; transform: rotate(0.00rad); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad);" src="https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/byshM0P40taVfn_oUMo__sdujY31bkkKf8o0tODJOLHaspdMtNcy-7d7p9ztKlFpbSPsHxFtTM5W126wsfdo1YA784Tj_L_RVOAqosdCeUA3yKG68gq-KI36RlKMUrxb1A" alt="" width="81px;" height="51px;" /></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">Step 2: </span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">Select one or more values from any number of the filter drop downs. &nbsp;The list of ideas will be filtered to only show ideas containing the specified values.</span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;"><img style="border: none; transform: rotate(0.00rad); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad);" src="https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/_PJ9GSnJTOSKvo85OC4FzRldRy144-y-e9pWrVdRgtVPu4HGeCCk7iYOv7ETyfPzvSOdYQcnhCVH9lsVYTWtpBwTznnvxmorIta1kCReGokQ57jMCr0_gld7Js7PGEv8mg" alt="" width="283px;" height="494px;" /></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">Note: This works in conjunction with searching and sorting. &nbsp;You can search, filter, and sort in any order, and the final result will obey all three.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 8pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 17px; font-family: ''Trebuchet MS''; color: #3d85c6; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">4.7.1 Clearing Filters</span></h3>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">To remove all of the filters at once and see the full, unfiltered list, click the clear filters button</span><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;"><img style="border: none; transform: rotate(0.00rad); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad);" src="https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/9Uv1xqyjEl4qMmou1dtXoizAlVEpR6-Dlc30LqJXEJygfFUGCmLkztd91CfIlKPxWhE57bGMlS6eHNEtRG-kXZTlwIG8POxr-kquYf0EaFtg7UyxfuZZoE693yGIDlaQBw" alt="" width="29px;" height="29px;" /></span><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">which can be found in the top right corner of the Filters section.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 0),
(11, '4. Workflows  -  4.8 Sorting ideas', '<p id="docs-internal-guid-c44a3040-e8af-6b15-9fbf-fedb581c965c" dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">You may be interested in seeing your ideas sorted in a certain way, to do so, use the Sorting section on the Search page.</span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;"><img style="border: none; transform: rotate(0.00rad); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad);" src="https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/7qeFjGqcA2vYA_up7ebSn56Fe6B9X_MsAwyOp2hzpj6UV5glToRwqqqi80v3S1ArbsWnpkH16d7yUe1sFyUgKjAXIoImvoBGSKAh6_DYN1mg6oqxUyqD5tFfpyfHegGD-w" alt="" width="259px;" height="112px;" /></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">Step 1: </span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">To search for an idea, click the </span><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">Search</span><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;"> button located on the navbar.</span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;"><img style="border: none; transform: rotate(0.00rad); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad);" src="https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/byshM0P40taVfn_oUMo__sdujY31bkkKf8o0tODJOLHaspdMtNcy-7d7p9ztKlFpbSPsHxFtTM5W126wsfdo1YA784Tj_L_RVOAqosdCeUA3yKG68gq-KI36RlKMUrxb1A" alt="" width="81px;" height="51px;" /></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">Step 2: </span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">Select a value to sort by. These values include Unsorted, Name, Community Partner, Idea created, Idea last updated, Project start date, and Project end date.</span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;"><img style="border: none; transform: rotate(0.00rad); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad);" src="https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/CjcoDlsaclXOTiqGEvUsV7qDtzGiDkN_uVaI7w8D8SMOD1kiSCXcIEEhhUq6-N0a3ui_XFhNEBQviGdHvUDHM-GMCjIXjkzBW5gsfW8zvSwrDgLo8u5wchBl-QwZtnRn3A" alt="" width="259px;" height="292px;" /></span></p>\r\n<p><br /><br /></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;"></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">Step 3: </span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">Select an order, either ascending or descending.</span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;"><img style="border: none; transform: rotate(0.00rad); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad);" src="https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/PAl88pzdtVPXZDXusI2APveDPPkJK9jPEfiKqFtW23dDMdQrG3ocoPqCxMpOeRHwJ_mzrz5OBbfKNFbFX2GX8Bt9nxB4EqC8tOyHk-leUWMnQIKmy8mFGwcq6y5Q5cxqTA" alt="" width="259px;" height="177px;" /></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">You can do Step 2 and Step 3 in either order. Sorting will be applied automatically every time Sort by and Sort order are changed. &nbsp;Unsorted is the default order the results are returned in, there is no different between Ascending and Descending. &nbsp;When sorting by Name or Community Partner, Ascending is alphabetical, and Descending is reverse alphabetical. &nbsp;When sorting by Idea created, Idea last updated, Project start date, or Project end date, Ascending is oldest dates to newest dates, and Descending is newest dates to oldest dates.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">Note: This works in conjunction with searching and filtering. &nbsp;You can search, filter, and sort in any order, and the final result will obey all three.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 0),
(12, '4. Workflows  -  4.9 Resetting your password', '<p id="docs-internal-guid-c44a3040-e8b0-a931-d00f-90f0e06b3f06" dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">If at any point you forget your password, or just wish to change it, follow the steps below:</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">Step 1:</span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">Go to the Login page via website address (URL) that has been provided to you by the host (in this case, probably UBC IT). If you are currently logged in, please logout. </span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;"><img style="transform: rotate(0rad); display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/aU5UxicoK9I8HlB_pcS_F6uOAAyjaM0UbUgeV8BWok0pJolLKBpZomuJTt4pXO8MK3zbTkaM_Vi5Nbrauu-TPLs3CL5hH7ogtCTraX28WyjLiXDVqM-qTrse3Sj23kI-MA" alt="" width="624px;" height="307px;" /></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">Step 2:</span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">Below the login button you will see a link labeled </span><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">Forgot Password? </span><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">that looks like this</span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 36pt; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;"><img style="border: none; transform: rotate(0.00rad); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad);" src="https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/NB1axYTot-Sm213vtetDewOZwoXn7hrZOVfHCxRMJLQkGs8wrTCFXFbEaOtRLPm4cLmrT9nKNhDlgZCCX8gSOSSTNXzYefvNW43bFPaTcHJpwxfbjyrw40Mt5wUVE01yIQ" alt="Forgot password.png" width="137px;" height="33px;" /></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">Click this link.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">Step 3.</span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">You will be re-directed to the Reset Password page (seen in the image below). It will ask you to give the email address, please enter the one you are attempting to login as then click </span><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">Reset Password</span><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;"> button.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;"><img style="border: none; transform: rotate(0.00rad); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad);" src="https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/BzVL8zwJ40rInKxm7o_zXZ3zNDTS2xKNJ4n21X6k0qcmqPVlJjedjJwpBgwICXPJNLozkQqgue2FW37NtFTkd_jPgHssrrvwyPNMMUKG5hDvA7PwlnUenkgrpiARayiMfg" alt="" width="368px;" height="202px;" /></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">Step 4: </span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">You should receive an email within a few minutes no-reply@cims.com The email should look similar to the one below. Inside this email will be a link. This link will direct you to a new page where you will setup your password for the account you just created. The link will only be valid for a period of 24 hours for security reasons. Please click the link.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;"><img style="border: none; transform: rotate(0.00rad); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad);" src="https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/DztVNCpM1IadcTzEWmwVSEXf2KRShPuG85-C-JufSUDX73yDodMFlRIwoGUJhKCOydsou0Sc9wQa7UyfWjDQlSfOrP3NG5pB-uM4TJuA31sYKGWa7WpNoB0xnRBJ1UtX2A" alt="" width="449px;" height="141px;" /></span></p>\r\n<p><br /><br /></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">Step 5:</span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">You should now be at the New Password page that looks like the image below. This page contains 1 field that you are required to fill out: your new password. This password must be between 8 to 32 characters in length. Once you&rsquo;ve entered your password, please click </span><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">Submit</span><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">. </span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;"><img style="border: none; transform: rotate(0.00rad); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad);" src="https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/3WxFOdCitxC3dd5GXbUq0L-Lwj5szoy_kSP5rlMVe6bMeE27ajuZeh1dmjud2_9TlCSQGGfIMZFCx2Quz5I32t0Nfa0Ylt8rSVRhPQNJNzqwv94qkayKsco7LdgNAKtqHA" alt="" width="367px;" height="188px;" /></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">Step 6:</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">You will be re-directed back to the Login page. You may now login with your new password. If this did not work, please attempt the process again or talk to an administrator. </span></p>', 0),
(13, '5. Admin workflows  -  5.1 Creating users', '<p id="docs-internal-guid-bb7c9443-e8b1-6ec0-3e83-1aa5e257bb6d" dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">Step 1: </span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">On the top of any page you will see a button that looks like this:</span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;"><img style="border: none; transform: rotate(0.00rad); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad);" src="https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/2crG4x1uLzLR3d4ZPr29sLMnnzSGGR1TsFChIj3-2TClAzlrLtjOS2nkDM7zgQ-OIliZuX6mEb0vpjmP_BlHId8oaEiiMtp4MCstPW1LKifC1Cwe2b_JWcwbfqVcT3XmCg" alt="management button.png" width="127px;" height="52px;" /></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">Click this button to show the drop-down list. Inside this drop-down, please select </span><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">User Management</span><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">.</span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;"><img style="border: none; transform: rotate(0.00rad); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad);" src="https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/REKro9sfk_N4YlbQfoQ-UGAR53norYeF_eK9SdTweCibhDoj5NBZ-IvWMQ1qYFl8aBI0ckbp93g6BONMRKBH27N1LZ2eVy5A6h7U6_TI4_816nnkod_tyLCOQ_XsC9rHIA" alt="management button open.png" width="186px;" height="143px;" /></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">Step 2: </span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">You should now be re-directed to the User Management</span><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">page which should look similar to the picture below. If you are not redirected to this page, please attempt Step 3 again. </span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;"><img style="transform: rotate(0rad); display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/AAHjDMkwuZ0-TidVoReY1w5sAbBh1cbpQ0k78kPYkh2w3NIgswceNKJNcH47uR63O2JvpnJ296CWWA6DzlduJ_YzmU0yMb1EqgGwyqV0PjyzV938K_GDYx0-QJdDYATXSg" alt="User Managment.png" width="624px;" height="293px;" /></span></p>\r\n<p><br /><br /></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">Step 3: </span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">It is time to create your own user. In the top right corner you should see an icon that looks like a person with a plus symbol, similar to this, </span><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;"><img style="border: none; transform: rotate(0.00rad); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad);" src="https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/1KkDBSlR3qePRqsUJQm_M46xymDqFbBIeOms3T4_wSr7EX7RZou9nqNIML9aUK9xf-gfaiYsdkch6x5bC__nbjaTNM02ESaf8WtJNhzF6PlHDa1m_MnwyCERt4EIRWb4Cg" alt="add a user.png" width="45px;" height="43px;" /></span><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">. Please select this button.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">Step 4: </span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">You should now be re-directed to a Create User page, just like the image below. You will see 3 fields which you will need to fill in: Name, Email, and Role. </span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;"><img style="transform: rotate(0rad); display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/-Bo3pFjUQWOwQXl0KnOjRba2CLvLkOCYdCqvFUfnAufExWJaCDnmKkPOQlNyPtJXZ2xxd8ZPb3C8VpAox5uCbhw9NG8qOvtVrtcWQ50esYarov0xd8ZhmxmBOHc3kzJ1Sg" alt="Create User.png" width="624px;" height="295px;" /></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">Name</span><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">: This will be the display name of the user you are creating. It will show anywhere that the user is referred to such as Idea Ownership, Comments, or Sharing (explained in </span><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: italic; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">Section 3.4 - My Page , Section 3.6 Commenting on an Idea, </span><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">and</span><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: italic; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;"> Section 3.7 Sharing an Idea </span><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">respectively).</span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">Email Address:</span><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;"> You will be required to enter a valid email address. It is vital that you use a real email account as an email will be sent to that address with steps to create a password.</span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 15px;