alue from by click the corresponding </span><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">Category Name.</span><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;"><img style="transform: rotate(0rad); display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/7sSbq4WNhP0KWieNZxa4sFQhGvReSJxb3lNEaDzK_vy9tZDkCEcXnstp__W7yoirUpo6335ec91dmbtmWc1gLbW1GTxZF9zM_deqeU0qiO8sk9aT2TqQ1rpX-f8O7C8dlw" alt="Screen Shot 2014-04-03 at 10.05.04 PM.png" width="624px;" height="261px;" /></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;"></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">Step 3: </span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">You will now be directed to a page that has the name of the category you selected at the top (in the image below we selected &ldquo;Type&rdquo;). On this page you will see a trash can icon which represents </span><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">Delete</span><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">. If you hover over this button, you should see a tooltip that says &ldquo;Delete&rdquo;. Please click this icon.</span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;"><img style="transform: rotate(0rad); display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/pwV8c7dfxiTl2zvY6rmjZ-GQMZRwqDq7hDTRjTfu2kuBgEpORiisYAJEB2nK_4H0kII6KOAc34WSm1PjXkX8Ko8YRyHeBURGX6cDjY9rgo-VupkmKWCuDi1hPrHLmvrMRg" alt="Screen Shot 2014-04-03 at 10.18.39 PM.png" width="624px;" height="231px;" /></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">Step 4: </span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">A new window will open that will ask if you are sure you want to delete the value (In this case the value is &ldquo;One-Time Project&rdquo;). Please click the </span><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">OK</span><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;"> button to delete this value.</span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;"><img style="border: none; transform: rotate(0.00rad); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad);" src="https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/dSEjJjqp60AuZtE5hDEmJ9yoqjgQmKpCrdkK2d9TMXRIxXugbUap6wnXcZxcXhFxRruXI-8fINNf1ZvUV_CPAjwiHjRctCcbztmoe2olMpcN7DuXo-el4jB6HgiUdXn2KA" alt="delete value.png" width="390px;" height="174px;" /></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">Step 5:</span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">You should not see delete value located in the list with all the other values. However, any idea that was using this value will still have the deleted value until updated.</span></p>', 1),
